"1/4 cup fat-free plain yogurt","1 tablespoon cider vinegar","1 tablespoon water","1/4 teaspoon kosher salt","  Freshly ground black pepper","1  (15-oz) can low-sodium chickpeas, rinsed and drained","2 1/2 cups sliced packed green cabbage","2  stalks celery, thinly sliced","2  carrots, peeled with a vegetable peeler into strips or thinly sliced, or 2 cups shredded carrots","2 tablespoons sesame seeds, toasted"